  - y-component: `cos(x₀)(sin(x₂)x₁ + cos(x₂)x₂) - sin(x₀)x₃`
  - z-component: `sin(x₀)(sin(x₂)x₁ + cos(x₂)x₂) + cos(x₀)x₃`
